(set: $steps to $steps + 1)

Which option is the best **verb IRI** for completion?

[[`completed`->QuizWrong]]
[[`http://adlnet.gov/expapi/verbs/completed`->QuizRight]]

:: QuizWrong
(set: $steps to $steps + 1)

<script>
if (window.tecaaXapi) {
  window.tecaaXapi.send(
    Object.assign(
      window.tecaaXapi.base(
        'http://adlnet.gov/expapi/verbs/responded',
        'responded'
      ),
      {
        result: {
          success: false,
          completion: false,
          response: 'completed'
        }
      }
    )
  );
}
</script>

Not yet. `completed` alone is not globally unique and should not be used as a raw identifier.

[[Try again->QuizIRI]]

